casebody.data:
No. 13-791. Supreme Court of the United States March 24, 2014.

John J. MOORES, et al., petitioners,
v.
David HILDES, Individually and as Trustee of David and Kathleen Hildes 1999 Charitable Remainder Unitrust Dated June 25, 1999.

The Solicitor General is invited to file a brief in this case expressing the views of the United States.
